metadata.name: Psy-Maya: Laxmi on Shrooms 🍄
metadata.description:
PsyMaya: Laxmi on Shrooms 🍄🔱

An ode to self healing through psilocybin. ⚛️
The image reflects Laxmi-the goddess of power and maya, draped in magnificent ornaments, standing on an illuminating lotus blessing the visitors by opening a window of ineffable mysteries. 🕉🍄🌸

3000 * 3000 pixels
